import React, { Component } from 'react' import { Container, Header } from 'semantic-ui-react' import { Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react' const ProjectDescription = () => (
Choose your fantasy soccer team

Welcome to our Fantasy Soccer Team Predictor! Let's see if you can pick a team to beat our AI!


⚽ A team is made up of 2 goal keepers, 5 defenders, 5 midfielders, and 3 forwards

⚽ Pick your fantasy soccer team based on a particular game week and see how your team does for that game week

⚽ Check out the table below to see player information based on a gameweek! Select a gameweek to see player's scores from the previous week

⚽ The table contains information such as the player's name, team, position, and away and home scores based on the selected game week
Select a gameweek and your team, and when you click submit, you can see how your team does compared to our AI. We have a table below to give you player information! In the table, you can see we show the player's name, team, position, and their away and home scores from the previous week selected based on the filter. Check out the team information in the table and go select your team! See if you can beat our AI! We will show your team's score and compare it to our AI's team!

) export default ProjectDescription
